      "date": "2018-10-10 01:27:27.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nFailed enforced test custom on RHEL 7.0/x86_64 uploaded by Onyx Autotest from onyx-30vm1: https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/27b19321-5496-4db0-8436-473e93a85ce2 ran 2 tests.  1 tests failed: lustre-initialization-1.",
